590
00:28:53,740 --> 00:28:54,800
Do you understand?

591
00:28:59,820 --> 00:29:02,380
Xue has become more and more serious recently.

592
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:04,940
He even asked us to write down our target school

593
00:29:04,940 --> 00:29:06,890
and stick it to the desk to encourage ourselves.

594
00:29:06,890 --> 00:29:09,060
It's obvious that he learned it from Ms. Xiao.

595
00:29:09,060 --> 00:29:10,250
Yes.

596
00:29:10,540 --> 00:29:13,140
How can we decide the target school so soon?

597
00:29:14,220 --> 00:29:15,660
Actually, I've almost made up my mind.

598
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:16,940
Anyway, for the major of journalism,

599
00:29:16,940 --> 00:29:19,300
the Sun Yat-Sen University is more suitable.

600
00:29:19,300 --> 00:29:20,300
I've also made up my mind.

601
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:22,620
The major of Geography at Qingbei University.

602
00:29:22,620 --> 00:29:23,680
What about you, Tu?

603
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:25,740
I have too many ideas.

604
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:27,400
I still need to think about it.

605
00:29:27,940 --> 00:29:28,940
Yin Zihan, you...

606
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:30,620
Ma'am.

607
00:29:30,620 --> 00:29:32,880
Yin Zihan has been abroad for two months.

608
00:29:35,220 --> 00:29:37,740
I miss the time we were together.

609
00:29:37,860 --> 00:29:38,860
I wonder

610
00:29:39,060 --> 00:29:40,520
how he's doing over there.

611
00:29:40,980 --> 00:29:42,980
He has started pursuing his dream.

612
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:45,510
But my prospects still remain undecided.

613
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:57,840
Can I really be admitted into a good university?

614
00:30:04,010 --> 00:30:05,620
How are your studies recently?

615
00:30:05,620 --> 00:30:07,750
Do you need me to tutor you face to face?

616
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:13,460
Happy birthday, Ling Chao.

617
00:30:11,660 --> 00:30:13,570
[Xiao Tu]

618
00:30:30,530 --> 00:30:31,990
[Nanjing University, Chinese]

