[There are 108 days before the college entrance exam]

621
00:30:50,930 --> 00:30:53,800
[Class 1, Senior 3]

622
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:38,500
Is it true that everyone already got a goal and a dream long ago

623
00:31:38,500 --> 00:31:39,500
except for me?

624
00:32:00,770 --> 00:32:01,740
Ling Chao?

625
00:32:09,220 --> 00:32:09,820
Excuse me.

626
00:32:10,300 --> 00:32:11,220
This is my seat.

627
00:32:12,020 --> 00:32:13,140
Don't be so petty.

628
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:14,660
Let's share the seat.

629
00:32:17,810 --> 00:32:18,500
Why are you here?

630
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:19,820
Aren't you in Yunhai?

631
00:32:20,140 --> 00:32:22,540
I was worried that someone would forget her own goal

632
00:32:22,540 --> 00:32:25,270
and couldn't get over her pessimistic feelings.

633
00:32:26,460 --> 00:32:27,860
That's right.

634
00:32:28,340 --> 00:32:29,940
Everyone has his own dream.

635
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:30,780
Only I don't have a dream.

636
00:32:30,780 --> 00:32:32,110
How can I not be anxious?

637
00:32:33,140 --> 00:32:34,380
Why do you think you don't have a dream?

638
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:35,660
Who always talked about

639
00:32:35,660 --> 00:32:38,120
going to and leaving school with me forever?

640
00:32:38,180 --> 00:32:39,650
You said that in kindergarten.

641
00:32:39,650 --> 00:32:40,740
Speaking of goals,

642
00:32:41,420 --> 00:32:43,580
you set up a goal earlier than all of them.

643
00:32:43,580 --> 00:32:45,090
That's different.

644
00:32:45,530 --> 00:32:53,880
[Excellent Class. Mobile Red Flag]

645
00:32:45,730 --> 00:32:46,700
Besides,

646
00:32:46,700 --> 00:32:48,300
is it because I don't want to go to Yunhai University?

647
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:49,940
The reason is that with my grades, there is a big gap

648
00:32:49,940 --> 00:32:51,200
between Yunhai and me.

649
00:32:52,660 --> 00:32:54,160
Don't think too much.

650
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:56,380
Just focus on one thing now.

651
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:57,620
Do you

652
00:32:58,420 --> 00:33:00,220
want to go to Yunhai University?

653
00:33:07,460 --> 00:33:08,860
Since you said yes,

654
00:33:10,020 --> 00:33:11,420
just go forward bravely.

655
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:16,220
When you were a kid, your godmother always said that

656
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:18,290
you learned everything slower than others, right?

657
00:33:18,290 --> 00:33:19,820
But when it comes to eating,

658
00:33:19,900 --> 00:33:22,300
you eat faster than anyone else, don't you?

659
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:24,980
How can you comfort me like this?

660
00:33:26,050 --> 00:33:26,740
Alright.

661
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:28,340
I mean,

662
00:33:29,140 --> 00:33:30,250
since childhood,

663
00:33:30,580 --> 00:33:32,380
you've been able to do the things

664
00:33:32,420 --> 00:33:33,820
which you want to finish.

665
00:33:34,980 --> 00:33:36,460
Just like when you were admitted into No.1 High School

666
00:33:36,460 --> 00:33:38,580
after overcoming so many difficulties.

667
00:33:38,580 --> 00:33:39,420
This time,

668
00:33:40,020 --> 00:33:41,150
you can make it, too.

669
00:33:44,820 --> 00:33:45,500
Can I...

670
00:33:46,340 --> 00:33:47,220
really make it?

671
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:51,900
I don't know whether others can make it.

672
00:33:53,420 --> 00:33:55,480
But your luck in exams is really good.

673
00:33:55,500 --> 00:33:56,140
So,

674
00:33:57,220 --> 00:33:58,700
just go forward bravely.

675
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:01,350
I'll wait for you in Yunhai.

676
00:34:12,350 --> 00:34:13,940
[Yunhai]

677
00:34:16,699 --> 00:34:17,460
[Yunhai]

678
00:34:19,020 --> 00:34:20,080
What are you doing?

679
00:34:20,250 --> 00:34:21,659
I'm writing down my own dream.

680
00:34:21,659 --> 00:34:22,739
Xue said that

681
00:34:22,770 --> 00:34:24,980
we could encourage ourselves by doing this.

682
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:26,780
But this is someone else's desk.

683
00:34:29,860 --> 00:34:30,739
Then let's leave now.

684
00:34:30,739 --> 00:34:31,980
I can buy you a cake.

685
00:34:31,980 --> 00:34:32,820
Let's celebrate your birthday.

686
00:34:32,820 --> 00:34:33,420
Let's go.

687
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:37,179
At this hour,

688
00:34:37,179 --> 00:34:38,510
