689
00:35:02,180 --> 00:35:05,480
[Excellent Class. Mobile Red Flag]

690
00:35:03,660 --> 00:35:05,190
Ling Chao, happy birthday.

691
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:09,860
No one eats a Wife Cake to celebrate his birthday.

692
00:35:09,860 --> 00:35:11,460
Just make do with it.

693
00:35:11,490 --> 00:35:13,260
Besides, it has a good meaning.

694
00:35:13,260 --> 00:35:15,860
Maybe you can really get a wife after eating it.

695
00:35:16,700 --> 00:35:18,140
I might as well find some fish flesh

696
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:19,100
