697
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:20,650
[Excellent Class. Mobile Red Flag]

698
00:35:20,090 --> 00:35:20,700
Wait.

699
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:21,820
Make a wish first.

700
00:35:23,860 --> 00:35:25,340
But there are no candles.

701
00:35:39,650 --> 00:35:40,260
All right.

702
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:45,580
Happy birthday to you.

703
00:35:46,220 --> 00:35:46,820
Happy...

704
00:35:47,660 --> 00:35:48,460
So soon?

705
00:35:49,460 --> 00:35:51,100
It looks like you decided what wish to make long ago.

706
00:35:51,100 --> 00:35:52,220
What wish did you make?

707
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:55,480
I hope that you can be admitted into your ideal university.

708
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,690
You're lying.

709
00:35:57,780 --> 00:35:58,380
Forget it if you don't want to tell me.

710
00:35:58,380 --> 00:35:59,710
Come on. Have some cake.

711
00:36:02,620 --> 00:36:03,750
Where are you going?

712
00:36:27,090 --> 00:36:28,220
Ling Chao, look.

