00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:35,340
It's true. Look.

717
00:36:39,260 --> 00:36:41,020
I regret not reading more books.

718
00:36:41,020 --> 00:36:43,860
All I can think about now is "How beautiful".

719
00:36:44,780 --> 00:36:45,540
Yes.

720
00:36:49,700 --> 00:36:50,560
How beautiful.

